{"tid":1977523,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［Pizza撚］點睇大pizza Paisanos Pizzeria","createTime":"2020-04-18T04:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T05:26:49.000Z","uid":215642,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2facaf05f38cc961c598379d571e95fb850690c","tid":1977523,"uid":215642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"12吋Pizza 最平$30已經飽到痴線<br />\n三個人食14吋都係$110左右<br />\n講緊成班開party 24吋都係二百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無記錯間野開咗大約10幾年好似冇加過價<br />\n<br />\n味道方Pizza面好撚入味，會即刻翻熱。小食方面麥樂雞同雞鎚都好味過好多市面，基本上價錢品質完全吊打市面幾間連鎖Pizza 鋪<br />\n<br />\n入邊員工完全講英文，好多鬼佬Abc食，可以感受中產生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個價位真心痴線，賺埋都唔夠點交租，究竟點生存咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y2B4zvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2B4zvM.png&h=52fab9bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a388567b55a6bb4faf3375cc4e06d9f3aff92e46","tid":1977523,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"搞手只求打個和"},{"pid":"2415ef4f83841fd8a4a51a351f74f3ee0e260ebb","tid":1977523,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"西貢果間有個abc識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504cf2024434a4c9651ec0e5406874fff16504d1","tid":1977523,"uid":128413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"不了 <br />\n食第一兩啖還好 食到之後又硬又乾 啲料又普通<br />\n勁似7仔啲即叮pizza"},{"pid":"16f1f6d9eabd246aed1073b8b2c04b9f3756db46","tid":1977523,"uid":6071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"超難食 食完成個覺得好滯"},{"pid":"9eb09e325529181010c9c0f202d964797a601485","tid":1977523,"uid":301962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"New York pi